title: Stanislav Juga
text:
Rhinocamera
I found a company Rhinocamera on the Internet. I needed to buy a lens for Nikon D750 - TAMRON 70-200mm f 2.8. It was a very good price. All terms and conditions of sale were tempting, so I ordered a lens - and I did not regret! I'm from Czech Republic.
It was a few days before Christmas. The consignment arrived from Germany to the Czech Republic for a staggering five days !! Perfectly packaged! I appreciate such a service. Lens okay. Communication with Rhinocamera is perfect. They immediately responded to the question, still communicate with me, even Czech.
Every such e-shop I highly recommend. There is no mistake!
Stanislav Juga
Czech Republic Å umperk
